{"tid":891139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隨時「骨肉相連」　美媽媽臍帶作首飾創商機","createTime":"2018-11-06T00:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T01:42:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83530b790b450b644ee90abc3cf173a05f4e26f0","tid":891139,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:54:17.000Z","msg":"不少孕婦在孩兒呱呱落地、剪斷臍帶一刻，都若有所失，感到不再與至親骨肉血脈相連。佛羅里達首飾設計師艾拉（Ruth Avra）自創「臍帶項鍊」，為媽媽們保留懷孕時「母子相連」的感覺。<br />\n艾拉於2012年初為人母，兒子出生後，肚臍位置殘留小部分臍帶組織，在7日至21日後自動剝落，但艾拉久久不捨得丟掉該臍帶末端。同一時間，她的一名朋友也剛產子，有相同經歷，認為臍帶是母子曾經相連的證據，十分珍貴，於是她忽發奇想，把臍帶製成項鍊，貼身保存，並開始在網路接訂單，為其他母親永久保存臍帶。<br />\n艾拉的項鍊以脫蠟法（lost wax casting）鑄造，每條設計隨着臍帶形狀而改變，獨一無二，要價200美元（約台幣6,142元）。在美國，另類品牌Speckled Milk早已提出用臍帶訂製戒指，還可以用人奶、毛髮、胎盤、人或寵物的骨灰，製成首飾。（北美中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_1840387b899ffbb88ec9744b23b873a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_1840387b899ffbb88ec9744b23b873a8.jpg&h=a8d18ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佛羅里達首飾設計師Ruth Avra自創「臍帶頸鏈」，為媽媽們保留懷孕時「母子相連」的感覺。翻攝Ruth Avra Instagram"},{"pid":"1b241d17f87a40924fc067740cdbd9623dbdf246","tid":891139,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"諗起有個切陰唇做首飾"},{"pid":"5f9910ccdb1184cd92e4f4e0a4a2bce42eb0bd40","tid":891139,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:07:09.000Z","msg":"收返來丟左佢<br />\n最後上淘寶買 交貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb8d6ac668a372b429dd47c0cabd5bd7e23b2a6","tid":891139,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b241d17f87a40924fc067740cdbd9623dbdf246","tid":891139,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"諗起有個切陰唇做首飾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d439bf63694ba82135a3cf31795d415537023ca","tid":891139,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:42:10.000Z","msg":"佛牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}